Dukey Flyswatter https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dukey_Flyswatter 0 Michael David Sonye (; born April 22, 1954), best known by his stage name Dukey Flyswatter, is an American actor, screenwriter and musician, recognized for his work on numerous low-budget B movies and as singer for the Los Angeles horror punk band Haunted Garage.
